nodes.text: Bille Doshun was a Human male present on Coruscant in 22 BBY. He was inside the Outlander Club when the Jedi Obi-Wan Kenobi and Anakin Skywalker were chasing Zam Wesell. Doshun wore an outfit of dark colors like black, maroon, and dark green, as well as black boots. His hair hung in two braids.
